    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and kept in a garage its whole life. You won't find a single scratch on it. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
