      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and babied since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014seriously, it's flawless! I'm only selling it because I'm moving, otherwise, I'd keep it forever. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
