    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2016 Porsche Cayman S is a definitive example of mid-engine precision, featuring the 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) and VarioCam Plus. The drivetrain is anchored by a 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission, providing seamless torque delivery to the rear wheels via an electronically controlled differential. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package, this vehicle offers active engine mounts and optimized shift logic for peak lateral acceleration. The chassis is structurally immaculate, retaining factory tolerances with no signs of heat cycling or stress fatigue. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers paired with vented, cross-drilled rotors showing no measurable wear. From the integrity of the vacuum lines to the pristine condition of the underbody aero-panels, this vehicle remains in absolute concours-grade mechanical state.",
